Query package info from registry

Usage: normalize package info [OPTIONS] <PACKAGE>

Arguments:
  <PACKAGE>  Package name to query (optionally with @version)

Options:
  -e, --ecosystem <ECOSYSTEM>  Force specific ecosystem (cargo, npm, python)
  -r, --root <ROOT>            Root directory (defaults to current directory)
      --json                   Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>              Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty                 Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact                Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help                   Print help
